name: Maul's Sith Speeder
Lore: 'Attain speeds of up to 600 kph. 3 meters long. Extremely difficult to control at high speeds. Dengar rode a similar swoop when injured in a race with Han at Agrilat.',
Text: 'May add Maul as driver. May deploy with Maul as a ''react''. During battle, Maul may disembark (place this vehicle in Used Pile) to cancel the immunity to attrition of a Jedi here. Immune to attrition.(Original concept by Ryan French - Seattle V-Lite 2005)(Errata Text - September 9th, 2009)',
